    <body>
        <section name="About the Wren:AM Project">
            <p>Wren:AM is an "all-in-one" access management solution providing
                strong and adaptive authentication, authorization, single sign-on (SSO),
                entitlements, federation and web services security.
            </p>
            <p>Wren:AM provides mobile support out of the box, with full OAuth 2.0
                and OpenID Connect (OIDC) support - modern protocols that provide
                the most efficient method for developing secure native or web-based
                mobile applications optimized for bandwidth and CPU.
            </p>
